flowchart Boarding a Merchant Ship
direction-lr

(Spot Sail green) -> [Hoist Colors] -> <In Range?>
  -yes-> [Fire Warning Shot] -> <Surrender?>
  -no-> [Give Chase] -> <In Range?>

<Surrender?>
  -strikes-> [Board Peacefully] -> [[Take the Cargo]] -> (Sail Away green)
  -fights-> [Grapple and Board red] -> [Storm the Deck] -> [[Take the Cargo]]
